## 🔑 Key Takeaways

- Understanding how computers work is essential before learning advanced cybersecurity concepts.
- The Client-Server model forms the backbone of modern internet communication.
- Virtualization allows multiple isolated systems to run on a single physical machine.
- Containers provide lightweight environments for application deployment.
- Cloud computing enables scalable, reliable, and cost-effective infrastructure.

